etal in nonmagnetic materials and might be relevant for pyrochlore oxides\nwith heavy transition-metal ions such as alloys of iridates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Jan 2015 15:04:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-16"}
